        %p
          Section 2 of the GAMSAT
          %sup ®
          exam consists of written responses to two sets of stimuli, commonly referred to as Task A and B. You will be presented with two set of quotes that are each related to a common theme.

        .highlight_box.gamsat-prep.mbot20
